title: KonishiPamphlet
author: Helleonov
pages:
#- Welcome, one and all, to Konishi Liquor Store, open since August 2021! Your patronage is very important to us. All brews we sell here are nothing short of perfect. Whether they are distilled, aged, or just fermented, all times and ingredients have been worked on tirelessly until 5    
#- stars have been reached. 

Inside, you will find, besides the chests with the brews, some lecterns with menus or buying guides. Feel free to read them and even take them home if you need more time to decide on your purchase. We want to make sure our clients
#- are completely satisfied! In case a brew's stock is over, or if you want to make a suggestion or a complaint, feel free to PM Helleonov or drop a written book in the mailbox of Fort Lapis to the north. Larger amounts for bars or other liquor stores can also be arranged with Helleonov. 
#- Feel free to take this pamphlet, there are plenty more in the back! Once again, welcome to Konishi Liquor Store, your go-to place for the best brews around!
#- 